<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>OpenLaw Certificate</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 2cm;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2c3e50;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .certificate-type {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #34495e;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .certificate-id {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .land-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .case-item {
            background-color: #fff9e6;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 2px solid #2c3e50;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .stamp {
            border: 2px solid #2c3e50;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 100px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .generated-date {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .status-flag {
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        
        .status-flag.ongoing {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            border-color: #dc3545;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        
        .status-flag.resolved {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            border-color: #28a745;
            color: #155724;
        }
        
        .status-flag.unknown {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-color: #ffc107;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .case-status {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            padding: 5px;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        .ongoing-case .case-status {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        
        .resolved-case .case-status {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        
        .unknown-case .case-status {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .case-details {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .party-info {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 3px solid #007bff;
        }
        
        .party-text {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .judgment-outcome {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px;
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border-left: 3px solid #28a745;
        }
        
        .outcome-text {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #155724;
        }
        
        .case-name {
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-top: 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .recommendation-high-risk {
            border-left: 5px solid #dc3545;
            background-color: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
        }
        
        .recommendation-low-risk {
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1);
        }
        
        .recommendation-caution {
            border-left: 5px solid #ffc107;
            background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
        }
        
        .recommendation-clear {
            border-left: 5px solid #28a745;
            background-color: rgba(40, 167, 69, 0.1);
        }
        
        .recommendation-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .recommendation-title-high-risk {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        
        .recommendation-title-low-risk {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .recommendation-title-caution {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        
        .recommendation-title-clear {
            color: #28a745;
        }
        
        .recommendation-message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .recommendation-details ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .recommendation-details li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">OpenLaw Kenya</div>
        <div>Land Due Diligence & Litigation Intelligence System</div>
    </div>

    <div class="certificate-type">
        
            CLEARANCE CERTIFICATE
        
    </div>

    <div class="certificate-id">
        Certificate ID: 3f103efb-9b14-4e91-908a-e420318ca185
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Land Details</div>
        <div class="land-details">
            <strong>Title Number:</strong> Esther Wanjira Kamau v George Chege Kamau [2019] KEELC 2706 (KLR)<br>
            <strong>LR Number:</strong> LR No Dundori/Miroreni Block 2/56 ; LR No. Dundori/Miroreni Block 2/56 <br>
            
            
            
            <strong>County:</strong> Unknown
        </div>
    </div>


    

    

    

    
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Search Results</div>
        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;">
            <strong>No litigation cases found</strong><br>
            This land parcel has no registered court cases in our system.
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="stamp">OFFICIAL</div>
        <div>This certificate is electronically generated by OpenLaw Kenya</div>
        <div class="generated-date">Generated on: 05 March 2026</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
